OL,3,C'I spoke out and was bullied for it'
OL,5,FA Fermanagh horse producer who says
OL,6,Fshe was bullied for speaking out
OL,7,Fagainst the man accused of the murder
OL,8,Fof Katie Simpson has said Johnathan
OL,9,FCreswell "could do no wrong" and there
OL,10,Fare still people who defend him.
OL,12,FLast week, a review into the the death
OL,13,Fof the 21-year-old exposed a series
OL,14,Fsystemic failures in safeguarding in
OL,15,Fthe equestrian industry.
OL,17,FSpeaking to UTV Karol Kelly claims the
OL,18,Fabuse in the industry is nothing new
OL,19,Fand girls have no choice but to
OL,20,Fprotect themselves.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
