OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778587868
OL,3,C'I spoke out and was bullied for it'
OL,5,FCreswell, 36, a showjumper was charged
OL,6,Fwith the 21-year-old Katie's murder.
OL,7,FAfter the first day of the trial he
OL,8,Ftook his own life.
OL,10,FCarol, who knew Creswell well, said:
OL,11,F"They hung on every word he said, he
OL,12,Fcould do no wrong. There was a huge -
OL,13,Fand still is to a certain extent - 'he
OL,14,Fdidn't do it' brigade out there."
OL,16,FFollowing the review into Katie's
OL,17,Fdeath, there have been calls for
OL,18,FStormont to come up with a dedicated
OL,19,Fequine safeguarding strategy.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
