CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778587868
OL,3,C'I spoke out and was bullied for it'
OL,5,FSpeaking about the industry Carol
OL,6,Fsaid: "Some of these trainers, it's
OL,7,Fmore important to them that their very
OL,8,Fexpensive horses are being trained.
OL,10,F"They're not too worried about
OL,11,FJonathan Creswell hitting someone a
OL,12,Fslap in the background, you know.
OL,13,FThere's a lot of eyebrows raised, but
OL,14,Fthere's a wee touch of 'well it's none
OL,15,Fof my business'.
OL,17,F"Unfortunately I'm not one of those
OL,18,Fpeople and I have got backs up and my
OL,19,Fjudgment of Jonathan Creswell and what
OL,20,FI know about him, I myself have got
OL,21,Fbullied as a result for speaking out."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
