CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778587868
OL,3,C'I spoke out and was bullied for it'
OL,5,FThe review commissioned by the
OL,6,FDepartment of Justice looked into the
OL,7,Fdeath of the 21-year-old County Armagh
OL,8,Fshowjumper in Londonderry in 2020.
OL,10,FIt found, Creswell, who was charged
OL,11,Fwith Katie's murder after trying to
OL,12,Fmake it look like suicide, was a
OL,13,Fpredator who hid in plain sight, using
OL,14,Funregulated yards as a hunting ground,
OL,15,Fand his abusive behavior toward Katie
OL,16,Fand others was accepted in the
OL,17,Fequestrian community.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778587868
OL,3,C'I spoke out and was bullied for it'
OL,5,FThe review stated, "Jonathan
OL,6,FCreswell's ability to act with
OL,7,Fimpunity was enabled by gaps in
OL,8,Fregulation/safeguarding".
OL,10,FThirty-seven more victims have now
OL,11,Fcome forward, including children as
OL,12,Fyoung as nine, claiming Creswell
OL,13,Fabused them too.
OL,15,FThe PSNI have also identified two more
OL,16,Falleged sex offenders within the
OL,17,Fequine industry.
OL,19,FCarol warns that there are certain
OL,20,Fthing to look for.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
